==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Agglutinant
<hw>Ag*glu"ti*nant</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>agglutinans</ets>, <ets>-antis</ets>, p. pr. of
<ets>agglutinare</ets>.]</ety> <def>Uniting, as glue; causing, or
tending to cause, adhesion.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>Any
viscous substance which causes bodies or parts to
adhere.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Agglutinate</ent>⟦br⟧
